        "$:/plugins/tg/layout/readme": {
            "text": "''Note:''<br>This plugin contains 'general' settings for the layout and is additionally required for my following plugins: ^^1^^

* Top menu
* Top-left menu (top + left menu)
* Toolbar (on top)
* Tiddlersbar
* ~TabStory (alternative tiddlersbar at top of story)
* Uptoolbar (toolbar above title)
* Tristate (tristate sidebar)

This plugin contains layout code common to the mentioned plugins and let you adjust:

!! Theme tweaks
* Sidebar layout
* Story left position
* Story top position
* Story right
* Story width
* Tiddler width
* Sidebar top position
* Sidebar width

!! Layout tweaks
* Checkboxes
** Display layout button (<<icn $:/plugins/tg/layout/images/layout>>)
** Search above story
** Toolbar to toggle editor toolbar + preview
** Sort recent results alphabetical
** Button to top of story river
** Hide description Tools tab buttons
** System tags tab
** Recent dates bold
** Sticky titles
*** Add sticky editor toolbar (when titles are sticky)
** Set tiddler toolbar above the tiddler title
** Tagging in view mode
** Field handling in view mode
** Setting type in view mode

* Other settings
** Color and height of the top bar (as a boundary for top menu, toolbar, tiddlersbar, etc.)
** Top padding of a tiddler
** Color for  displaying the  'active' state of some toggle buttons

Settings for the layout can be found in ''~ControlPanel > Appearance > [[Plugin tweaks|$:/plugins/tg/layout/tweaks]]'', also available via the 'Adjust layout' button (<<icn $:/plugins/tg/layout/images/layout>>) in the Toprightbar.

|borderless|k
|^^^1^^ |&nbsp;&nbsp;|All these plugins contain a 'Settings' tiddler tagged with $:/tags/plugin-tweaks and will display - when installed - a tab under 'Plugin tweaks'.|

<<<
''Note:''<br>@@color:red;A sticky editor toolbar works ''only'' well in non-preview mode!.@@
<<<",
